flowchart TD
    A([bamboo_answer called]) --> B

    B{Content-free follow-up?\ne.g. 'Tell me more'}
    B -- "yes + history present" --> C[Reformulate RAG query\nuse last real question from history]
    B -- no --> D

    C --> E
    D[Topic guard\nkeyword check → LLM if ambiguous] -- rejected --> F([Return rejection message])
    D -- allowed --> E

    E[Deterministic routing — no LLM\nregex extracts task_id · job_id · keywords]

    E --> G[panda_log_analysis\njob_id + failure keywords]
    E --> H[panda_job_status\njob_id only]
    E --> I[panda_task_status\ntask_id present]
    E --> J[panda_doc_search\n+ panda_doc_bm25\nno ID found]
    E -. fallback .-> K[LLM planner\nbamboo_plan]

    G --> L
    H --> L
    I --> L
    J --> L
    K -. fallback .-> L

    L[execute_plan]
    L --> M[LLM synthesis\ncall_llm → natural-language answer]
    M --> N([Response returned])

    style K fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#aaa,stroke-dasharray:4 3
    style K color:#555